com.example.sickar.main.helpers

Class BarcodeDataCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.sickar.main.helpers.BarcodeDataCache

  • public class BarcodeDataCache
extends Object
    Data class to hold barcode information retrieved from the SICK AR backend service. Uses a list to keep track of the order of retrieved barcodes from latest to oldest. (Newest items are place in front) Holds the data associated with a barcode in a MAP Singleton so one cache persists throughout the entire app.
